---
title: Pan-Seared Gnocchi with Pesto, Green Beans, and Sun-Dried Tomatoes
description: Searing gnocchi in the pan creates irresistible crispy edges. Tossed with fragrant pesto, sautéed mushrooms, and sun-dried tomatoes, you’ll be fighting for the last bite.
